.SH NAME
~~man-name~~
.SH DESCRIPTION
~~app-description~~
.SH KEYS - ALL PUZZLES
.SS p:
Preview the puzzle image.
.SH KEYS - JIGSAW PUZZLE
.SS 1-3:
Select layer. Selected or dragged pieces will be moved to the new layer.
.SS Left and Right Arrow Keys:
Rotate the piece. Rotation only works if a single piece or connected group of pieces is being dragged.
.SS Shift:
Add to multi-select.
.SH KEYS - SPINNING TILE PUZZLE
.SS Shift:
Change rotation direction. Tiles normally rotate clockwise.
